  {'subject': 'Mathematics', 'year': 2019, 'question': "A kite is flying at a height of 60m with a string of length 100m. Find the angle of elevation of the kite.", 'options': ['36.87°', '53.13°', '30°', '45°'], 'correctIndex': 0, 'explanation': "sin θ = 60/100 = 0.6 → θ ≈ 36.87°."},
